# Desktop app (Tkinter GUI):This app provides an AI-generated summary that explains current weather conditions.

# Environment Setup Guide

# 1. Create a virtual environment
# python -m venv venv

# 2. Activate the virtual environment
# .\venv\Scripts\Activate

# 3. Install require library
# python -m pip install -r requirements.txt 

# 4. python gui_app.py

# 5. deactivate 
# leave the virtual environment and return to normal system Python

=============================================================
# pip → installs packages [pip is Python package installer]

# -m → ensures correct Python environment [-m is run a module as a script]

# requirements.txt → list of dependencies
